					    				    			<div class="post_header_wrapper">
    									<h1 class="post_title">“The Final City.” A Poem by Samer Abu Hawwash, translated by Huda Fakhreddine</h1>
					<h3>“by your small bed / torn apart by monsters, / I stand naked, / stripped of myself / and of everything.”</h3>
				</div>
				<div class="post_detail">
			    	May 24, 2024&nbsp;
			    							By&nbsp;<a href="https://lithub.com/author/samerabuhawwashhudafakhreddine/">Samer Abu Hawwash and&nbsp;Huda Fakhreddine</a>
								    					        <div class="post_comment_count"><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i><span class="dsq-postid" data-dsqidentifier="237307 https://lithub.com/?p=237307">2</span></div>
				    
			    	<div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"><span class="share-text">Share:</span><div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-icon sd-sharing"><div class="sd-content"><ul><li class="share-facebook"><a rel="nofollow" data-shared="sharing-facebook-237307" class="share-facebook sd-button share-icon no-text" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-final-city-a-poem-by-samer-abu-hawwash-translated-by-huda-fakhreddine%2F&t=%E2%80%9CThe%20Final%20City.%E2%80%9D%20A%20Poem%20by%20Samer%20Abu%20Hawwash%2C%20translated%20by%20Huda%20Fakhreddine" target="_blank" title="Share on Facebook"><span class="sharing-screen-reader-text">Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)</span></a></li><li class="share-twitter"><a rel="nofollow" data-shared="" class="share-twitter sd-button share-icon no-text" href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?via=lithub&text=%E2%80%9CThe%20Final%20City.%E2%80%9D%20A%20Poem%20by%20Samer%20Abu%20Hawwash%2C%20translated%20by%20Huda%20Fakhreddine&url=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-final-city-a-poem-by-samer-abu-hawwash-translated-by-huda-fakhreddine%2F" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Twitter"><span></span><span class="sharing-screen-reader-text">Click to share on Twitter (Opens in new window)</span></a></li><li class="share-google-plus-1"><a rel="nofollow" data-shared="" class="share-google-plus-1 sd-button share-icon no-text external" href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Flithub.com%2Fthe-final-city-a-poem-by-samer-abu-hawwash-translated-by-huda-fakhreddine%2F" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Google+"><span></span><span class="sharing-screen-reader-text">Click to share on Google+ (Opens in new window)</span></a></li><li><a href="#" class="sharing-anchor sd-button share-more"><span>More</span></a></li><li class="share-end"></li></ul><div class="sharing-hidden"><div class="inner" style="display: none;"><ul><li class="share-linkedin"><a rel="nofollow" data-shared="" class="s